{"tid":467180,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【高度壓迫感】全程直擊GoPro被熔岩吞噬前的情景","createTime":"2017-11-13T09:22:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-05T01:00:25.000Z","uid":2547,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f778c536cab28726082fac2b5478756fd343c359","tid":467180,"uid":2547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T09:22:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cOKYipjKVmE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcOKYipjKVmE&d=%2FYMK0%2FgWmQ5%2F85T3GOZOddtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=bb7e7b37\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cOKYipjKVmE</a><br />\n火山熔岩流到埋身，你敢不走嗎？一部攝影機無路可退之下，以第一身角度拍下熔岩流至的一刻，更奇的事，大家有機會目睹這難得一見的景象。<br />\n<br />\n夏威夷火山國家公園一個旅行團的導遊斯托姆（Erik Storm）表示，他的GoPro攝影機掉進火山裂縫，他作了最壞打算，用地質鎚破開岩漿後凝固而成的岩石，試圖撿回攝影機「屍骸」。<br />\n斯托姆撿回攝影機，以為經過1,000℃熔岩的洗禮，攝影機一定不能操作，但奇蹟出現，攝影機捕捉到橙紅色熔岩「殺埋身」以至烈燄在鏡頭前燃燒的情況，而且片段可以取回並播放，讓大家可安然觀看熔岩流過來的時刻。<br />\n<br />\n唔明點解咁都無壞到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過d 熔岩殺到埋身個陣真係好緊張"},{"pid":"b2beab38056297f3c8381551e1555f7bb5a4f986","tid":467180,"uid":2547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T09:51:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d2b719fd1131eeb4623a15fca25776d50fc0d95","tid":467180,"uid":34252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T10:06:10.000Z","msg":"哇.... 咁誇張"},{"pid":"650defb88105033621ced071ff60e59e8e6eb4d2","tid":467180,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T12:33:43.000Z","msg":"GoPro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">應該用嚟做廣告</span></span>"},{"pid":"88cd0b2a4af10fa24d2e250fd18eaf51d4d5bbca","tid":467180,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T01:00:25.000Z","msg":"REMOVED"}]}